<div id="review_2793587852" class="review" itemprop="reviews" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Review">
  <link itemprop="url" href="https://www.goodreads.com/review/show/2793587852" />
    <a title="Katie Lumsden" class="left imgcol" href="/user/show/8190907-katie-lumsden"><img alt="Katie Lumsden" src="https://images.gr-assets.com/users/1607448164p2/8190907.jpg" /></a>

  <div class="left bodycol">
    <div class="reviewHeader uitext stacked">
        <a class="reviewDate createdAt right" href="/review/show/2793587852?book_show_action=true">Apr 21, 2019</a>

      <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person">
        <a title="Katie Lumsden" class="user" itemprop="url" name="Katie Lumsden" href="/user/show/8190907-katie-lumsden">Katie Lumsden</a>
      </span>

        rated it
        <span class=" staticStars notranslate" title="really liked it"><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10">really liked it</span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p0"></span></span>



        

    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer2793587852" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer12821923387419258286">Another great fun Agatha Christie! I really enjoyed this one, and would highly recommend it. More of an adventure mystery than a murder mystery, with wonderful characters and a fun plot. I&apos;m definitely going to be reading more of the Tommy and Tuppence series in the future.</span>
  <span id="freeText12821923387419258286" style="display:none">Another great fun Agatha Christie! I really enjoyed this one, and would highly recommend it. More of an adventure mystery than a murder mystery, with wonderful characters and a fun plot. I'm definitely going to be reading more of the Tommy and Tuppence series in the future.</span>
  <a data-text-id="12821923387419258286" href="#" onclick="swapContent($(this));; return false;">...more</a>

